Just out of curiosity... You're using & instead of && to avoid short-circuiting?

84:14-84:15
Fri Feb 05 11:38:54 2016 +0000
Author: Alexandre Rames <1052304@85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889>
Parent: 918f4c7c_aff8b99f
